00:21:37,556 --> 00:21:41,286
lots of people who use
keyboards without using vision,


301
00:21:41,746 --> 00:21:46,496
both sighted typists
and blind typists.


302
00:21:46,826 --> 00:21:50,356
More recently, one of the
fathers of the internet,


