00:21:59,086 --> 00:22:02,636
for a solution that would
allow them to communicate


306
00:22:03,046 --> 00:22:06,486
without using hearing.


307
00:22:07,666 --> 00:22:12,796
And to communicate from afar.


308
00:22:12,886 --> 00:22:14,446
Disability drives innovation,


309
00:22:14,496 --> 00:22:17,316
not just by non-disabled
inventors but by people


310
00:22:18,236 --> 00:22:20,596
with disabilities as well.


311
00:22:20,596 --> 00:22:23,926
Vinton ended up developing one
of the earliest email protocols,


312
00:22:24,916 --> 00:22:27,756
and electronic mail
was one way for them


313
00:22:27,756 --> 00:22:30,066
to communicate from afar.


314
00:22:31,026 --> 00:22:34,216
And now, just about
everybody uses email,


315
00:22:35,106 --> 00:22:36,526
and sends text messages.


316
00:22:37,516 --> 00:22:42,066
Solutions designed with
disability in mind end


317
00:22:42,066 --> 00:22:44,046
up benefiting the
entire community.


318
00:22:44,646 --> 00:22:50,106
And central to innovation
is exploration.


